    <div id = "main text">
        <h1><center>Chiara Home</center></h1>
        <p style = "font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif";>
            Chiara Home is dedicated to the Spirit of Saint Clare of Assisi, who is known for her care of the outcase by providing both food and hospitality.
            Chiara Home desires to provide that same care to those people among us who have been identified as having a developmental difference or special need.
        </p>
        <p style = "font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif";>
            Chiara Home strives to undertake those activities which will promote both a gentle and home-like atmosphere so that all persons in our care may experience a 
            place of rest and a time of total acceptance.
        </p>
        <p style = "font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif";>
            Chiara Home provides out-of-home respite care services to families caring for an individual with a developmental disablity, mental disorder
            and/or other special needs.
        </p>
        <p style = "font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif";>
            In this way, we seek to provide families, supportive assistance so that institutionalizing their disabled loved ones can be prevented. It is also
            our goal to prevent abuse and neglect of disabled indivudals and help families remain together as functioning units within out community.
        </p>
    </div>

